Fatal and autodie

This distribution provides 'autodie', a lexical equivalent of
'Fatal' for Perl 5.10.  The distribution also upgrades the Fatal
module to contain better diagnostics and reporting.

This distribution REQUIRES Perl 5.10 or later to run.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc autodie
    perldoc Fatal

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Fatal

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Fatal

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Fatal

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Fatal


